# PDP Lifecycle — product boundary

This repo is **PDP Lifecycle**, a greenfield Vistral app. Do not assume Supply kanbans, property pipelines, settlement, or Reno unless the user explicitly asks to port them.

- Add features under `app/` and `lib/` for PDP Lifecycle domains only.
- Reuse `components/ui/`, design tokens (`app/prophero.css`), and `.cursor/skills/`.
- Supabase: new tables need migrations + RLS (see `11-migrations.mdc`).
